  63:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c **** 
  64:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****           Function HAL_SPI_RegisterCallback() allows to register following callbacks:
