  66:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) RxCpltCallback        : SPI Rx Completed callback
  67:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) TxRxCpltCallback      : SPI TxRx Completed callback
  68:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) TxHalfCpltCallback    : SPI Tx Half Completed callback
  69:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) RxHalfCpltCallback    : SPI Rx Half Completed callback
  70:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) TxRxHalfCpltCallback  : SPI TxRx Half Completed callback
  71:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) ErrorCallback         : SPI Error callback
  72:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) AbortCpltCallback     : SPI Abort callback
  73:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) SuspendCallback       : SPI Suspend callback
  74:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) MspInitCallback       : SPI Msp Init callback
  75:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) MspDeInitCallback     : SPI Msp DeInit callback
  76:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****           This function takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle, the Callback ID
  77:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****           and a pointer to the user callback function.
  78:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c **** 
  79:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c **** 
  80:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****       (#) Use function HAL_SPI_UnRegisterCallback to reset a callback to the default
  81:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****           weak function.
